{"tid":2430941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本聲優加持！京都念慈菴蜜被炒貴6倍","createTime":"2021-03-03T09:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T10:22:08.000Z","uid":31314,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"308ebbad4b99ad0143e63a8c8d88311372d5f5e2","tid":2430941,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"正所謂「物離鄉貴，人離鄉賤」，香港有不少本土老字號產品，去到外國一樣有價有市。好似早前日本朝日電視台節目《林修の今でしょ！講座》，邀請咗9位聲優大談工作秘辛及保養喉嚨方法，當中森久保祥太郎提到當自己聲音狀態不好時，會服用京都念慈菴枇杷膏，更表示最愛長條形的獨立包裝，工作前吃服用一包，即可舒緩喉嚨沙啞問題，而其他聲優紛紛附和吃過超有效，更被節目封為「聲優必備品」。<br />\n<br />\n連聲優們都大讚，節目播出後，唔洗講日本當地就出現搶購潮，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">日本Amazon一樽京都念慈菴蜜煉川貝枇杷膏150毫升賣成￥2,350(約港幣$176)</span></strong></span>，但<strong><span class=\"gold\">香港Watsons只係賣緊$30.9</span></strong>，足足炒貴近6倍，都咪話唔和味！不過炒還炒，Twitter唔少網民都好奇地問，究竟京都念慈菴係香港定台灣牌子? 事實上，香港藥房業家謝兆邦於1946年正式在香港設立「京都念慈菴總廠有限公司」，直到1961年在台灣設另一間廠，現時全球只有兩間廠房，可以話係香港之光啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HPQ73oJ2qS8q6C_0uRMKVg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/d820f910-7b03-11eb-b79b-bc1a87beb521\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHPQ73oJ2qS8q6C_0uRMKVg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2Fd820f910-7b03-11eb-b79b-bc1a87beb521&h=de84107b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u7Bo4bwuK7ldm163LO1.Gg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/d86ad350-7b03-11eb-aff7-5016c4318b9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fu7Bo4bwuK7ldm163LO1.Gg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2Fd86ad350-7b03-11eb-aff7-5016c4318b9f&h=02ea7e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XRqI6IUGpYx2HgsQkiNXpQ-